                            I agree to the processing of my personal data for the purpose of responding to my inquiry. <span class="text-red-500">*</span>
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-modern py-3 font-semibold">
                        <i class="fas fa-paper-plane mr-2"></i>
                        Send Message
